@startuml IRouter_removeLiquiditySingleTokenExactOut
actor User
participant Router
participant Vault
participant Hooks

== Initiation ==
User -> Router: removeLiquiditySingleTokenExactOut(pool, tokenOut, exactAmountOut, maxBptAmountIn, wethIsEth, userData)
note right: User calls Router to remove liquidity with exact token out.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L257-L279

== Vault Unlocking ==
Router -> Vault: unlock(encoded params)
note right: Router encodes RemoveLiquidityHookParams and calls Vault.unlock.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L263-L278\n**Code Citation (Vault)**: Vault.sol#L191-L197

== Remove Liquidity Hook ==
Vault -> Router: removeLiquidityHook(params)
note right: Vault executes Router's removeLiquidityHook.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L292-L327

== Remove Liquidity Logic ==
Router -> Vault: removeLiquidity(RemoveLiquidityParams with kind=SINGLE_TOKEN_EXACT_OUT)
note right: Router calls Vault.removeLiquidity for single-token exact out removal.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L294-L302\n**Code Citation (Vault)**: Vault.sol#L1042-L1102

alt shouldCallBeforeRemoveLiquidity == true
    Vault -> Hooks: onBeforeRemoveLiquidity(sender, pool, maxBptAmountIn, minAmountsOutScaled18, balancesLiveScaled18, userData)
    note right: Vault calls hook (if enabled) for pre-remove liquidity logic.\n**Code Citation (Hooks)**: HooksConfigLib.sol#L234-L242
    Hooks --> Vault: true
    note right: Hook returns true, signaling success.\n**Code Citation (Hooks)**: HooksConfigLib.sol#L239
end alt

Vault -> Vault: computeRemoveLiquiditySingleTokenExactOut(balancesLiveScaled18, tokenOutIndex, exactAmountOut, totalSupply, swapFeePercentage, pool)
note right: Vault calculates the BPT amount to burn for the exact token out.\n**Code Citation (Vault)**: Vault.sol#L1072-L1080\n**Code Citation (BasePoolMath)**: BasePoolMath.sol#L336-L392

alt shouldCallAfterRemoveLiquidity == true
    Vault -> Hooks: onAfterRemoveLiquidity(sender, pool, amountsOutScaled18, amountsOutRaw, bptAmountIn, balancesLiveScaled18, userData)
    note right: Vault calls hook (if enabled) for post-remove liquidity logic.\nMay adjust amountsOutRaw if enableHookAdjustedAmounts is true.\n**Code Citation (Hooks)**: HooksConfigLib.sol#L244-L252
    Hooks --> Vault: true
    note right: Hook returns true, confirming success.\n**Code Citation (Hooks)**: HooksConfigLib.sol#L249
end alt

Vault --> Router: bptAmountIn, amountsOut, returnData

== Token Transfer (Single Token) ==
alt wethIsEth == true and tokenOut == WETH
    Router -> Vault: unwrap WETH to ETH
    note right: If wethIsEth is true and tokenOut is WETH, Router unwraps WETH to ETH.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L314-L316
    Vault -> User: transfer ETH
    note right: Vault transfers ETH to user.\n**Code Citation (Vault)**: Vault.sol#L199-L212
else
    Router -> Vault: sendTo(tokenOut, user, amountsOut[tokenIndex])
    note right: Router instructs Vault to send the specified token to user.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L318-L320
    Vault -> User: transfer tokenOut
    note right: Vault transfers the specified token to user.\n**Code Citation (Vault)**: Vault.sol#L199-L212
end alt
note left: Only the specified tokenOut is transferred; other amountsOut are zero.

== Vault Settlement ==
Vault -> Vault: check _tokenDeltas == 0
note right: Vault ensures all transient debts are settled.\n**Code Citation (Vault)**: Vault.sol#L167-L189
Vault --> Router: encoded result

== Router Finalization ==
Router -> User: bptAmountIn
note right: Router returns the amount of BPT burned to user.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L279
note left: Delivers bptAmountIn to user, concluding the operation.

@enduml